    "Section 3 deals with the fundamentals of HSI.",
    "Section 4 provides an overarching introduction about the state of art in deep learning with an extension of HSI application of each technique for food analysis.",
    "Section 5 provides extensive application of HSI for food analysis creating an intuition for future collaborations using HSI and deep learning for enhanced accuracy and precision.",
    "Section 6 lays out a practical framework for undertaking the task of applying deep learning using hyperspectral images for food analysis.",
